{"tid":970536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國開抓了！「翻牆」罰比吸毒還重","createTime":"2019-01-06T02:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T08:09:54.000Z","uid":225846,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aba632fbb219bed25145375296774ba23916cf20","tid":970536,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國廣東韶關南雄市公安局近日對一名「翻牆」的朱姓網友開罰<br />\n，理由為「擅自建立、使用非法定信道進行國際聯網」，處以罰款人民幣1000元（約新台<br />\n幣4500元），被發現竟比違法吸毒罰的多一倍，有網友諷刺：「吸毒自取滅亡，翻牆中共<br />\n滅亡」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpAZ9P2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpAZ9P2q.jpg&h=4567adca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有中國網友發現，違法吸毒（右）被處以的罰款金額比翻牆（左）來得低。（圖擷取自廣<br />\n東公安執法信息公開平台）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpH2g7zu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpH2g7zu.jpg&h=145ffb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東一名朱姓網友因使用翻牆App而遭罰。（圖擷取自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPaixDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPaixDA.jpg&h=6b0d37bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有另一名重慶市的黃姓網友，近日也因「翻牆」被當地警方傳喚。（圖擷取自推特）<br />\n<br />\n據行政處罰決定書上資訊，這名朱姓網友因自去年8月起，頻繁使用藍燈（lantern pro）<br />\n軟體進行翻牆上網，被官方查獲開罰。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後有網友好奇在「廣東公安執法信息公開平台」網站上查看相關內容，發現另一<br />\n名違法吸毒的陳姓民眾被處以罰款人民幣500元，竟比翻牆罪行少一倍，讓網友在推特上<br />\n疑惑表示，「翻牆比吸毒嚴重？」有人則解釋：「吸毒自取滅亡，翻牆中共滅亡。兩權相<br />\n害取其輕，兩權相利取其重。」<br />\n<br />\n另有網友在推特指出，重慶市近日也有一名翻牆的黃姓網友收到警方傳喚通知，更讓中國<br />\n網友們人心惶惶，指出「以後每天的翻牆，戰戰兢兢」。"},{"pid":"9ed055935b1e0b9c8e8fe7f40e6234c7a66fc847","tid":970536,"uid":106835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:11:09.000Z","msg":"吸毒罰咁少？"},{"pid":"0a24d7c3e2e47c1e790ebf04e0c61f7dd1c8a36d","tid":970536,"uid":181797,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:11:12.000Z","msg":"應該槍斃"},{"pid":"28ab192b39e04b20e3e0f4b6cb90c3f6122a4a8a","tid":970536,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"習種有所謂七不講，十六條<br />\n<br />\n翻牆接觸西方思想<br />\n<br />\n係支共眼中同接觸毒品一樣"},{"pid":"505b8d1db5a926ece01a8abc790fda637d7bd145","tid":970536,"uid":64710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"翻牆之後會見到真理之門"},{"pid":"de0e284fecd3df094fd5b194d3ec96279114c5c3","tid":970536,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"601e1788592af78c7dceaecab886d21ff02753cf","tid":970536,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"做五毛就可以合法翻牆"},{"pid":"1fe5ecd906d2b0686cad724a821122a5ceb78975","tid":970536,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"剩係畀五毛翻牆洗版?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df718a0628378532186338ee68f66abd236d0b04","tid":970536,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"吸毒罰五<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7d14a711560411bf56f65c1df77d179aa000b6","tid":970536,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df718a0628378532186338ee68f66abd236d0b04","tid":970536,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"吸毒罰五<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"百"},{"pid":"ab8663032bf28073d9d6ac856267dd2a40be3cab","tid":970536,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"香港都應該啦 一國喔 拉晒班連登仔 咁多爹"},{"pid":"cf0cfabd03e02c4ad16d35655d7c93a0da835aa7","t